nested if- Defining if block inside another if block is called nested if.
       syntax-     
                 if(condition)
                 {
                     if(condition)
                     {
                        statement;
                     }
                       else
                       {
                          statement;
                       }
                       
                 }
                         
                  else
                        {
                            if(condition)
                            {
                            statement;
                            }
                            else
                            {
                              statement;
                              }
                        
                        
                        
                        }
